{"tid":630371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屈人非禮","createTime":"2018-04-15T14:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T14:30:00.000Z","uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b61e10b9f7ffe56b3e5250dba9b7ec77d9bfc1","tid":630371,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10160412232435245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10160412232435245%2F&d=4vOZNDDNR%2Fo7m4EIcyw%2BPHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b230617e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10160412232435245/</a><br />\n<br />\n好事唔怕人知！做得出，就預左有人講，雖然事件發生在馬鞍山，但唔知主角幾時有機會途經大埔，比大家知道下，未必係壞事。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：朋友傳來訊息，「明屈事件簿」<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於2018年4月14日，大约下午17:45，在81 C巴士内 (往馬鞍山方向)，著黑恤衫條仆街男子，當時佢個女用物件敲打櫈，發出噪音，坐前面一名青年望佢個女一眼，兩公婆(相中仆街)就鬧該青少年兇佢個女，條男仆街就撩青少年打交，及聲稱報警，事後個青少年想落車，嗰男仆街用腳攔住唔畀個青少年落車，個男仆街仲話個青少年非禮佢老婆要報警，屈人。<br />\n<br />\n當時有人睇到整個過程，睇不過眼條仆街屈人，立即出聲指責個男仆街，屈青少年非禮佢老婆 (相中女人)，其後個男仆街，見有人做證人指責佢，佢即刻想落車逃走，青少年叫司機唔好開門，要報警，其後警員到，個男仆街又話 青少年只係想非禮佢老婆。整件事如果冇他人出嚟做證，兩公婆就會恰該青少年或者屈佢。 最後兩公婆仆街，都在馬鞍山落車。"},{"pid":"011d271566b98646e3efa85c450d9b4f0e4f6e1d","tid":630371,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"心態幾醜惡先會咁屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d04267ef84cac2fdaa23c21851c2b9662e0b26c","tid":630371,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283076074ed1caef56d19d351b3adce0a3613471","tid":630371,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/224107_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F224107_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=05a2698f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"527e8e3339690dd17922535b7c6330a56470fd11","tid":630371,"uid":3738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"個男個樣一睇就知無賴唔係好人,相由心生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cee5234bdca44faf879c9040e3ce474089b8a2a","tid":630371,"uid":3738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/182638_b14ea7a42d272a6be8f1818b9503ff40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F182638_b14ea7a42d272a6be8f1818b9503ff40.png&h=7da4b3d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfb見到forward,幫下佢地出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba536ea3856057456f7d3e6885ea71acab990c6f","tid":630371,"uid":3738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c1d7d113d2fea61bc186a62c996671ceb5b800","tid":630371,"uid":3738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f091a722bea00d90ba05ab6812ab22dd8a085b58","tid":630371,"uid":101507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"睇睇下心諗個男做乜鳩無啦啦仆街，原來係男仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1e2fb1fff607402aba2ef63aa6c67d3a12431d","tid":630371,"uid":3738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbc7465864ea645342ea524cac3130cf943de09","tid":630371,"uid":3738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04